37  public class MS936_OLD    extends Charset
38      implements HistoricallyNamedCharset
39  {
40  
41      public MS936_OLD() {
42          super("x-mswin-936-OLD", null);
43      }
44  
45      public String historicalName() {
46          return "MS936";
47      }
48  
49      public boolean contains(Charset cs) {
50          return ((cs.name().equals("US-ASCII"))
51                  || (cs instanceof MS936_OLD));
52      }
53  
54      public CharsetDecoder newDecoder() {
55          return new Decoder(this);
56      }
57  
58      public CharsetEncoder newEncoder() {
59          return new Encoder(this);
60      }
61

64       * These accessors are temporarily supplied while sun.io

68       * are made extinct these will be unncessary and should be removed
69       */

75          return Decoder.index2;
76      }
77      public short[] getEncoderIndex1() {
78          return Encoder.index1;
79      }
80      public String[] getEncoderIndex2() {
81          return Encoder.index2;
